Ronnie O'Sullivan beat Craig Steadman 10-3 in the first round of the World Snooker Championship at The Crucible on Wednesday . 
  The five-time world champion had trouble with his shoes and was seen playing in socks on Tuesday . 
  He could face a small fine for breach of dress code at the tournament . 
  The 39-year-old beat Mark Williams 10-2 in his first round match . 
 